snippet.title: Ludum Dare: Repulsor Trailer - Pod-racing Game
snippet.description:
DOWNLOAD NOW: http://bit.ly/1ZSKfqR
Repulsor is a racing game insipired by the Star Wars pod-racer. The game was made in 72 hours for the Ludum Dare 34 by 7 devs.

JOIN US NOW, give your feedbacks:
Official Website: https://bit.ly/IronEqual 
Facebook: https://bit.ly/facebook-IronEqual 
Twitter: https://bit.ly/twitter-IronEqual

Trailer made by Benoit Cassin
